{"tid":1795251,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞和街掃黃行動 拘21名內地女子","createTime":"2019-12-23T17:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T08:48:26.000Z","uid":35348,"like":141,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"1d62285dd5830df220eed616196e5fcd4c7de391","tid":1795251,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:49:51.000Z","msg":"警方觀塘及秀茂坪警區特別職務隊聯同入境事務處人員，根據線報及經深入調查後，昨早上約11時展開代號「孤影」（LONESHADOW）及代號「萬里達」（MILESMETER）的掃黃行動，突擊搜查區內輔仁街、崇仁街、瑞和街、康寧道及偉業街一帶，共拘捕21名年齡介乎23至45歲持雙程證的內地女子，涉嫌違反逗留條件。被捕女子現正被扣留調查，稍後將交由入境事務處跟進。"},{"pid":"9a6fdff40da925d40f880d96fd2066fdfdd153fe","tid":1795251,"uid":70888,"like":308,"dislike":4,"score":304,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:54:31.000Z","msg":"黑警又有免費大陸雞屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但黑警最終都係生癌死落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df0dba2257e9bff2fe0466ae8e967ec7667958ea","tid":1795251,"uid":72334,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"9a6fdff40da925d40f880d96fd2066fdfdd153fe","tid":1795251,"uid":70888,"like":308,"dislike":4,"score":304,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:54:31.000Z","msg":"黑警又有免費大陸雞屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但黑警最終都係生癌死落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:55:40.000Z","msg":"最驚佢唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a9d162c0c78352ca8a098d2042f6fb62c19dab0","t